### Development Commands

#### Dependency Management
```bash
# Installing project dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Adding a new dependency
pip install package_name && pip freeze > requirements.txt
```

#### Code Generation
```bash
# Generating code from schemas
python -m src.tools.code_generator --schema schema.json --output output_dir
```

#### Build Tools
```bash
# Building project
python -m build
```

### Testing Commands

#### Unit Testing
```bash
# Running all tests
pytest

# Running specific test file
pytest tests/unit/test_file.py

# Running tests with coverage
pytest --cov=src tests/
```

#### Integration Testing
```bash
# Running integration tests
pytest tests/integration/

# Running end-to-end tests
pytest tests/e2e/
```

### Deployment Commands

#### Containerization
```bash
# Building Docker image
docker build -t agentic-fleet:latest .

# Running Docker container
docker run -p 8000:8000 agentic-fleet:latest
```

#### Environment Setup
```bash
# Setting up virtual environment
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # On Unix/macOS
.\.venv\Scripts\activate  # On Windows
```

### Maintenance Commands

#### Debugging
```bash
# Checking logs
tail -f logs/app.log

# Debugging with Python debugger
python -m debugpy --listen 5678 --wait-for-client app.py
```

